## Installation

```bash
pip3 install jj==2.0.0-dev.1
```

## Usage

### No App

```python3
import jj

@jj.match("*")
async def handler(request: jj.Request) -> jj.Response:
    return jj.Response(body="200 OK")

jj.serve(port=8080)
```

### App

```python3
import jj

class App(jj.App):
    @jj.match("*")
    async def handler(request: jj.Request) -> jj.Response:
        return jj.Response(body="200 OK")

jj.serve(App(), port=8080)
```


